### List of Books

GET http://localhost:4004/book/Books

### Fetch Specific Book
GET http://localhost:4004/book/Books(5)

### Add Book

POST http://localhost:4004/book/Books HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{  
"bookId": 2,
"title": "3 idiots",
"descr": "Comedy",
"stock": 11,
"price": 250,
"rating": 4,
"amount": 0
}


### Update Book

PUT http://localhost:4004/book/Books(bookId=2) HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{  
"bookId": 2,
"title": "dangal",
"descr": "Comedy",
"stock": 11,
"price": 250,
"rating": 4,
"amount": 3
}

### Delete Book

DELETE http://localhost:4004/book/Books(bookId=2)
